  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Boil a kettle</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Trim the <strong>asparagus</strong>, discarding the woody ends</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Chop the<strong> asparagus tips</strong> away from the stalks and set aside</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Roughly chop the <strong>stalks</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">and </span>bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Once boiling,</span> cook for an initial 4-5 min </p>\n<p>After 4-5 min add the <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">chopped asparagus</span> </strong>and cook for a further 4-5 min or until <span class=\"text-highlight\">tender</span> with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy cooking water </strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">While the pasta is cooking, cut the <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Separate the<strong> white crab meat</strong> from the <strong>brown crab meat</strong> with a spoon (you’ll use the white meat at the end!)</span></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half </p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks </p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot over a low heat with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 3-4 min until starting to soften</p>\n<p>Add the <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">Chinese rice w</span>ine</strong> and give <span class=\"text-highlight\">everything</span> a good mix up</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>brown crab meat</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<span class=\"text-highlight\"> mix to combine</span> – this is your <strong>crab sauce </strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong> to the <strong>crab sauce</strong> with <span class=\"text-highlight\">100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span></span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and the <strong>juice </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> </span><strong>lemon </strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Give everything a good mix up until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</span></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Remove the pot</span> from the heat and gently stir through the <strong>white crab meat </strong>and <strong>chopped parsley </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">– this is your<strong> crab, chilli &amp; lemon spaghetti</strong></span></p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges </p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2199.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<span class=\"text-highlight\"> <strong>crab, chilli &amp; lemon spaghetti</strong></span> with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong> to the side</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Season with a good grind</span> of <strong>black pepper</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
